*Steps for Making this system*
1. create folders like Attendance, trainer, dataset, datacollector, trainedmodels, GUI, Recognizer, harcascade.
2. download harcascade file which i have provided in the repo.
3. run the data_collector.py and collect the dataset and create your own dataset for your model.
4. once the dataset is created, then run trainer.py and train the model for the dataset. it will provide you with labels and trainer.ynl file in trainermodels folder.
5. then run the recognizer.py and recognize the face you have in the camera.
6. add it into csv file of attendance.
7. create GUI for the system from main_gui.py then you will get the interface for the system.
